<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3544:3550'><span class='krp-note'>三/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3550:3573'>小成之卦八震巽下為主坎離中為主艮兌上為主此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3573:3596'>因乾坤交易而定也震一陽巽一隂下為主兊二陽艮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3596:3619'>二隂中為主乾三陽坤三隂上為主此因隂陽消長而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3619:3642'>定也艮兊或主上或主中者以乾坤之交而言則主上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3642:3665'>畫故遯二隂主二剥五隂主五艮之中畫為主也臨二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3665:3682'>陽主二夬五陽主五兊之中畫為主也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3682:3709'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0072', 'WYG', '001-11b' );" name="001-11b" class="pb">[001-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='3709:3732'>大成之卦六十有四復姤一陽一隂主初臨遯二陽二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='3732:3755'>隂主二泰否三陽三隂主三大壯觀四陽四隂主四夬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='3755:3772'>剥五陽五隂主五乾坤六陽六隂主上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='3772:3795'>乾坤為主之卦四乾坤主上否泰主三　乾坤父母也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='3795:3818'>其尊無上故自主其重卦合卦而不復為他卦主者猶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='3818:3841'>黄鐘大吕二律之獨尊但自為宫而不復為他卦役也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='3841:3864'>坎離為主之卦二十有八坎離屯鼎需晉比大有蹇睽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='3864:3887'>井噬嗑節旅十有四卦主五蒙革訟明夷師同人解家</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='3887:3914'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0072', 'WYG', '001-12a' );" name="001-12a" class="pb">[001-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='3914:3937'>人困賁渙豐未濟既濟十有四卦主二　坎離得乾坤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='3937:3960'>中畫自主其重卦合卦而又各主十二卦所主倍於震</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='3960:3983'>巽艮兊四卦者貴中也故卦之有坎離者必以坎離為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='3983:4000'>主惟無坎離者然後震巽艮兊為主也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4000:4023'>震巽為主之卦十有六震巽大壯觀小過中孚豫小畜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4023:4046'>八卦主四復姤无妄升益恒隨蠱八卦主初　艮兊為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4046:4069'>主之卦十有六艮兊頤大過大畜萃六卦主上謙履咸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4069:4091'>損漸歸妹六卦主三遯臨二卦主二剥夬二卦主五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4091:4118'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0072', 'WYG', '001-12b' );" name="001-12b" class="pb">[001-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4118:4141'>震巽艮兊四卦自主其重卦合卦而又各主六卦半於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4141:4149'>坎離之所主也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4149:4154'>乾　泰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4154:4159'>坤　否</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4159:4182'>坎　屯　需　比　蹇　井　節　蒙　訟　師　解</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4182:4191'>　困　渙　未濟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4191:4213'>離　鼎　晉　大有　睽　噬嗑　旅　革　明夷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4213:4227'>同人　家人　賁　豐　既濟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4227:4254'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0072', 'WYG', '001-13a' );" name="001-13a" class="pb">[001-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4254:4277'>　以上乾坤坎離四正不易之卦為主者凡三十有二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4277:4281'>　卦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4281:4301'>震　復　大壯　小過　豫　无妄　恒　隨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4301:4321'>巽　姤　觀　　中孚　小畜　井　益　蠱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4321:4341'>艮　遯　剥　　頤　　謙　大畜　咸　漸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4341:4362'>兊　臨　夬　　大過　履　萃　　損　歸妹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4362:4385'>　以上震巽艮兊二變反易之卦為主者凡三十有二</span><br/>
